ading\nto a simplified deep learning model and shorter the classification response\ntime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Dec 2019 08:56:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Dec 2019 01:30:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-11"}
